%h2 upload an old account with diaspora import!

%p
  all of your posts and friends
  %b from an existing diaspora export file
  will be imported with a new diaspora username.
  we will let your friends know that you switched pods.

= form_tag '/users/import', :class => 'not_cool', :multipart => true do

  %p
    = label_tag 'user[username]'
    = text_field_tag 'user[username]'
  %p
    = label_tag 'user[email]'
    = text_field_tag 'user[email]'
  %p
    = label_tag 'user[password]'
    = password_field_tag 'user[password]'
  %p
    = label_tag 'user[password_confirmation]'
    = password_field_tag 'user[password_confirmation]'

  = file_field 'upload', 'file'
  = submit_tag "Upload"
%br
%br

= link_to "back to signup", new_user_registration_path

